{
  "title": "Language-group Differences in Very Early Retirement in Finland",
  "abstract": "The purpose of this paper is to study very early retirement as an indicator for poor health, with focus on a comparison between the two language groups in Finland. Extensive longitudinal data are analysed with the help of random effects probit models.",
